newsitem.title: USA: CSCE Brazil differential coffee stocks unchanged.
newsitem.headline: CSCE Brazil differential coffee stocks unchanged.

text.p: The amount of coffee stored in warehouses and certified for delivery against Coffee, Sugar and Cocoa Exchange's Brazilian Differential futures contract was 863 60-kg bags as of August 30, unchanged from the previous week.

The coffee was housed solely in New Orleans. There were no stocks in either New York or San Francisco warehouses. There were no bags pending classification or certification in New York, New Orleans or San Francisco.
